headline: THE BOCA RATON PRESENTS ARTISANS OF WINE & FOOD - BACK FOR A BOLDER, BIGGER SECOND EDITION IN PARTNERSHIP WITH NAPA VALLEY VINTNERS
summary: Artisans of Wine & Food returns to South Florida's iconic The Boca Raton, January 15-18, 2026, once again bringing together 100+ of Napa Valley's most sought-after vintners, 20+ Michelin-starred and celebrated chefs, and a lineup of signature experiences that set a new benchmark for luxury, taste, and philanthropy. The second annual event is once again in partnership with Napa Valley Vintners, along with presenting sponsor Capital One.
